Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.00,0:01:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(131,281)\fs20\fad(600,900)}在变换的季节中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.12,0:01:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么长时间没结果的比赛还真少见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.79,0:01:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全成了消耗战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.20,0:01:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一面承受着强烈的横向G力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.80,0:01:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一面持续着极度的紧张状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.93,0:01:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对肉体与精神的负担都非同小可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.42,0:02:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更何况在这样棘手的赛道上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.03,0:02:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一般人早就呕吐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.72,0:02:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耐力成了胜负的关键啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.78,0:02:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能确定的 就是先失去注意力的人会输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.92,0:02:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和美就这么回埼玉的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.86,0:02:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也许再也见不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.26,0:02:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么办才好? 怎么办才好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.75,0:02:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这句话 如果连这句话都不说出来...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.30,0:02:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然也不能改变什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.32,0:02:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可我要说“喜欢和美”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.82,0:02:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.17,0:02:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个...我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.33,0:02:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三轮来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.79,0:03:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两人都干劲十足啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.58,0:03:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看得我手都痒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.19,0:03:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,LEVIN也和第一轮先行时不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.37,0:03:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有两下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.49,0:03:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.14,0:03:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和刚才的跑法完全不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.02,0:03:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快得出奇 完全不留余地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.29,0:03:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一轮我并没想留手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.93,0:03:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不清楚道路状况的最初一轮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.68,0:03:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用百分之百的实力跑是山道常识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.26,0:03:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过这轮就全力甩开你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.49,0:03:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都到这地步了实在不想输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.53,0:04:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何都要咬住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.28,0:04:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,86好不容易肯听话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.83,0:04:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.24,0:04:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从没这么强烈地想赢过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.33,0:04:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为对手同样是86吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.40,0:04:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之一定要用这辆车来赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.78,0:04:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.03,0:04:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千钧一发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.36,0:04:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一不留神真的会很危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.46,0:04:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是输了就算完的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.22,0:05:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话说回来 我是疲倦了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.60,0:05:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才开始就感觉抓不准路线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.64,0:05:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道...是轮胎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.47,0:05:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偏偏这时...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.62,0:05:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,后轮坚持不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.66,0:05:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是后轮抓地力下降了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.47,0:05:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,形势不妙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.84,0:05:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有轮胎毫无办法解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.42,0:05:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然拼到了这个地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.71,0:05:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能还是不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.89,0:05:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会就此输掉吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.02,0:05:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.34,0:05:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的节奏应该下降了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.71,0:05:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却为什么没被前面的车拉远?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.89,0:06:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.25,0:06:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 只有这样才想得通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.43,0:06:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对方也发生了和我一样的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.01,0:06:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对方的车轮也打滑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.55,0:06:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是第四轮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.37,0:06:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出人意料地成了消耗战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.02,0:06:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对方的后轮衰减也应该很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.47,0:06:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马力提升的话 这负担也会直接作用在轮胎上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.70,0:07:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彼此都是提升了马力的车 以同样的节奏持续跑到现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.07,0:07:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轮胎在差不多的时候不行了也不足为奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.09,0:07:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厉害 从后面看得很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.81,0:07:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,条件越恶劣 他的跑法反而越娴熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.03,0:07:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但对方也是有血有肉的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.53,0:07:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先忍受不住的人就会输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.08,0:07:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在比的是耐力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.85,0:08:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轮胎抓地力下降容易打滑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.80,0:08:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反而更容易了解这车在极限领域中的跑法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.35,0:08:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毫无别扭感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能随心所欲的操控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.55,0:08:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能驾驭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是我的86
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.94,0:09:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基本是靠油门来转向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.65,0:09:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这点和以前的车一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.28,0:09:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但和以前不同之处...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.37,0:09:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽情让它滑行的话就能清楚了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.95,0:09:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白这车的跑法了 老爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.96,0:09:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个...现在是第几轮了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.02,0:10:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,头脑中也一片空白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经相当疲倦了 但...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.09,0:10:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.86,0:10:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且到了这种时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.64,0:10:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相比之下 后追的人比先行的人更费神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.14,0:10:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使速度稍有差异也无法在这条赛道超车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.48,0:10:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要输也只有在后面追时被甩开而输掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.84,0:10:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是说前面跑的时候是不会输的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.80,0:10:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接着是有塌方的弯道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.22,0:10:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎么努力 旁边也没空隙能插进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.87,0:10:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总算能喘口气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.76,0:10:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞧着吧 在你忍耐不住出现失误前...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.97,0:10:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要跑多少轮我都奉陪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.71,0:11:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.29,0:11:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,砂土磨得比刚才平了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.44,0:11:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别做蠢事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.91,0:11:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是不可能超车的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.46,0:11:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么人啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.31,0:11:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.59,0:12:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没注意到每次有车横排而过就会削去塌方的砂土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.61,0:12:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且从那微小缝隙精准入弯的技术...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.11,0:12:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙...不是一般的厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.74,0:12:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速度慢了下来 看来有结果了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.50,0:12:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁赢了? TRUENO还是LEVIN?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.88,0:12:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是TRUENO 拓海赢了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.06,0:12:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.29,0:12:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海那小子真行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.91,0:12:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.28,0:13:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥他们回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.64,0:13:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.56,0:13:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.72,0:13:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.31,0:13:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总算平安归来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.68,0:13:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是筋疲力尽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.87,0:13:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上来吧 和美 回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.29,0:13:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.65,0:13:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那再见了 树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.01,0:14:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连再见都说不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.84,0:14:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的还能再见吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.46,0:14:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.29,0:14:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.37,0:14:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比赛怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.63,0:14:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赢是赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.11,0:14:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗...你真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.21,0:14:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就完全不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.63,0:14:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海你费心为我着想 还帮我制造机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.91,0:14:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可想说的话 我一句都没说出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.68,0:15:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天起就一直在想和美的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.60,0:15:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我从喜欢上和美后开始明白...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.44,0:15:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喜欢一个人竟然会这么痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.19,0:15:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦喜欢上了就会认真起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.14,0:15:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以无力挽回之时心脏就会感到撕裂般的痛楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.10,0:15:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也许会笑我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.61,0:15:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.44,0:15:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能理解?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.25,0:16:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很晚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.37,0:16:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离送货只剩一小时了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.97,0:16:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了 我要好好睡会儿 到时叫醒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.06,0:16:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.67,0:16:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真没想到车会那么好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.68,0:16:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 老爸 有空的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.44,0:16:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次教教我有关引擎的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.54,0:16:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是吹的什么风?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.40,0:16:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了自己严重欠缺的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.09,0:17:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海 树那小子有点奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.59,0:17:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正迟早会知道 我就说了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.27,0:17:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此 事情成了这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还以为进展很顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.70,0:17:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又变回孤独车手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.59,0:17:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.15,0:17:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.71,0:18:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了? 不是回埼玉了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.73,0:18:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时太急了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.80,0:18:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来拿留在这儿的行李
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.62,0:18:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.21,0:18:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但留下的不只是行李
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.10,0:18:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之前太过匆忙 没好好和你道别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.97,0:18:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和美 现在有时间吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一小时就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.35,0:18:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没问题 可你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.06,0:18:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他说个人原因要早退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.33,0:18:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.91,0:18:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挥洒青春啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.14,0:18:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这事对他来说比什么都重要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.16,0:18:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.40,0:18:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你女朋友夏树好像开始打工了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.45,0:18:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们俩进展如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.59,0:18:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茂木?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.07,0:19:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶季也要结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.02,0:19:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会忘记秋名的红叶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.47,0:19:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每次叶子变红时一定会想起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.03,0:19:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来群马遇到的朋友们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.22,0:19:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些人中最特别的他 虽然有些臭美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.29,0:19:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但却比谁都温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.36,0:19:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,经常鼓励我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.54,0:19:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小我一岁 就像是弟弟般的男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永远...绝对...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.98,0:19:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.70,0:20:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.42,0:20:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.95,0:20:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要在这儿用餐吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见 和美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.83,0:20:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然说不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.20,0:20:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我是喜欢你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.27,0:21:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥 群马选拔队的编制怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.30,0:21:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,候选人已有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.18,0:21:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接着就看他同不同意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.68,0:21:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能总是输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.54,0:21:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Emperor也好 秋名86也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.00,0:22:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定会来复仇的

